BREAKING: Hillary Gardee was allegedly forced to draw money before being shot in the head execution-style. This is according to the Gardee family.  The family’s spokesperson, Sinawo Tambo, said she was made to draw R1 300 before she was murdered. ALSO READ: EFF mourns loss of Hillary Gardee He said the forensic team had found a bullet lodged in the back of Hillary’s head and believe there is a deeper motive to the murder. He said the Gardee family also have some concerns regarding the way the crime scene was handled by the police. This is a developing story. Lowvelder will update its readers as soon as more information becomes available. ALSO READ: EFF Julius Malema will show “ugly side of EFF” if they catch Hillary Gardee’s killer